{"tid":1821093,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[行動]1月12和你讀，無人知啊，要大家幫手啊 - 本日重開","createTime":"2020-01-12T04:14:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-12T05:51:21.000Z","uid":205927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"22c217a09ef5b91c8de22c47983efcfb70e09cf1","tid":1821093,"uid":205927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T04:14:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iXUq8Hf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiXUq8Hf.jpg&h=b7224a6d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eO3SOHj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeO3SOHj.jpg&h=0e060f92&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n1月12 和你讀 免費派書活動<br />\n地點 灣仔ACO 2-7PM<br />\n2-4PM 為新書聚，可以黎攞書同問吓問題，睇下自己可以點幫手<br />\n&mdash;<br />\n請各區有心人自備背囊或環保袋<br />\n帶書返自己區 搵黃店、連儂放書<br />\n&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n知己知彼，百戰百勝，<br />\n不知己，豈能勝？<br />\n<br />\n了解哲學思維有助邏輯上嘅辨證，<br />\n在這本首次被翻譯為中文的書中，<br />\n與起義有關的概念多不勝數，<br />\n書是免費的，<br />\n知識是無價的。<br />\n<br />\n請大家多多支持，呢本書我哋一班文學、翻譯、藝術人士譯左好耐㗎啦！自資印咗5000本，好需要你哋嘅幫忙去18區放書！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n現正招募<br />\n<br />\n香港八大大學站員<br />\n站員職務：<br />\n1.指定時間到指定地點攞書、海報、膠紙 (有可能安排到直接將書送去各大學校園，如果安排到，麻煩報名嘅同學喺校園接應)<br />\n2.返自己校園揀位貼海報同擺書<br />\n3.影張靚相，影條靚片<br />\n4.搞掂<br />\n<br />\n香港十八區站員<br />\n站員職務：<br />\n1.指定時間到指定地點攞書、海報、膠紙<br />\n2.返自己區搵獨立嘅黃書店，問下可唔可以攞免費書，佢話得就留低書同海報<br />\n3.仲有書同海報淨底嘅話可以放喺連儂牆<br />\n4.影張靚相，影條靚片<br />\n5.搞掂<br />\n<br />\n有意嘅話可以喺個chat度留言，或send個訊息俾Admin @hktazz ，身邊有大學生嘅朋友不妨幫我地宣傳下，麻煩晒大家！<br />\n<br />\n本書我哋印緊5000本，一月9或10號就出到貨。再提多次，書係免費嘅！"},{"pid":"dbaf27e87e1d66bec3e2b19010c784f82ba31008","tid":1821093,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T04:16:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">美國議員講野又無人理啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n響task2呀 幫手啦上唔到千呀</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>Twitter組24小時keep住更新</strong></span><br />\n幫手retweet <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n㩒入👉<a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=uClJ75VMDgyJ2T8QnpTVXZuyGkzLGvEkvhYecc72uXM%3D&h=40049995\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a><br />\n然後打<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"> /task2</span></strong></span> 攞任務"},{"pid":"c73882fcb2c304e7655465d78720c1fcf9beb557","tid":1821093,"uid":49018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T04:19:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e4eb14b6bf4fcf2aedbc6df817032fdb300c38a1","tid":1821093,"uid":205927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T04:24:19.000Z","msg":"推！！"},{"pid":"1da60d5c4ca11d8190fe829a7d5c9b2d483a7d61","tid":1821093,"uid":210727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T04:24:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a80fa59f84e77ab543cac2ebc90a0c6d83f97be7","tid":1821093,"uid":26441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T04:25:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf6e4563a9f68189d724c4f0d6e993d82170e641","tid":1821093,"uid":161985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T05:51:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e096e7f39046c84163031898b6e82a2bf482f1ba","tid":1821093,"uid":205927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T05:51:21.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}